    "en": {
      "title": "A man was arrested for smuggling Kerala ganja in a luxury vehicle",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suspect who smuggled Kerala ganja from Karpiti to Colombo in a luxury vehicle was arrested today (06).",
        "The said vehicle was intercepted with the help of the Navy at the checkpoint in Karambai area of \u200b\u200bKapiti Colombo main road and conducted search operations.",
        "Nuraichol police said that 212 kg of Kerala Ganja was seized from the said vehicle.",
        "A 32-year-old man from Colombo Grandpass has been arrested on suspicion.",
        "They said that steps are being taken to produce the arrested suspect, the seized Kerala ganja and the luxury van used for smuggling in the Puttalam court."
      ],
